item.title: Hello World
item.description: The title seemed like a good fit for my first blog post. Hello to all the readers out there if there are any. “Cricket”…..“Cricket” Well anyways, today will be my last day in Vancouver before I head to University. I am filled with both excitement and anxiety of moving away but I’m sure everything will work out. This will be where I am going to start blogging and presenting myself. It may change in the future but for now this is all I could whip up in the short time before School.
